00:28:17,129 --> 00:28:19,089
Our key tech department staff

569
00:28:19,089 --> 00:28:20,010
was only just told.

570
00:28:20,369 --> 00:28:21,650
Just a retired teacher.

571
00:28:21,690 --> 00:28:22,809
How'd she get such info?

572
00:28:23,369 --> 00:28:24,490
Who knows? Let's go.

573
00:28:33,490 --> 00:28:35,609
(I explained
the work-related injury claim process)

574
00:28:35,609 --> 00:28:36,569
(to her thoroughly.)

575
00:28:37,170 --> 00:28:39,650
I also highlighted some key points

576
00:28:39,650 --> 00:28:41,730
for labor dispute negotiations
with employers.

577
00:28:42,690 --> 00:28:44,690
It was on our way to the hospital.

578
00:28:44,930 --> 00:28:45,890
I didn't know Jun An

579
00:28:45,890 --> 00:28:47,170
would represent Yiaiwan.

580
00:28:53,730 --> 00:28:54,250
Mr. Zhou.

581
00:28:54,250 --> 00:28:56,490
There was a themed party
at the bar that night.

582
00:28:56,490 --> 00:28:58,089
All attendees were regular patrons.

583
00:28:58,410 --> 00:28:59,809
The bartender there

584
00:28:59,809 --> 00:29:01,010
took lots of pictures.

585
00:29:01,170 --> 00:29:02,049
Including some of Zhu.

586
00:29:02,289 --> 00:29:03,930
I compiled those photos and evidence

587
00:29:03,930 --> 00:29:05,529
and sent everything to your email.

588
00:29:10,970 --> 00:29:12,930
Do you want to say something to me?

589
00:29:16,170 --> 00:29:17,089
It might be

590
00:29:17,490 --> 00:29:18,930
inappropriate for me to say it.

591
00:29:19,569 --> 00:29:20,170
Well...

592
00:29:20,450 --> 00:29:21,089
Well...

593
00:29:21,210 --> 00:29:22,369
About

594
00:29:22,769 --> 00:29:25,089
your personal connection
with Guo Xiaoyu.

595
00:29:26,010 --> 00:29:26,568
Just...

596
00:29:29,049 --> 00:29:30,250
Lawyer through and through.

597
00:29:30,690 --> 00:29:33,129
One sentence needs 100 qualifiers.

598
00:29:33,129 --> 00:29:34,730
And pre-written disclaimers.

599
00:29:35,170 --> 00:29:37,010
Terrified of misspeaking.

600
00:29:37,650 --> 00:29:38,650
Are you asking me

601
00:29:38,650 --> 00:29:40,490
if being so close to Guo Xiaoyu

602
00:29:41,210 --> 00:29:42,970
means my actions will hurt her?

603
00:29:44,529 --> 00:29:46,690
Not something
you should ask professionally.

604
00:29:47,289 --> 00:29:48,089
So

605
00:29:48,170 --> 00:29:49,369
is this concern for me?

606
00:29:55,970 --> 00:29:57,769
If now's bad, I'll come back later.

607
00:29:58,329 --> 00:29:59,129
We're done. Come in.

608
00:30:05,329 --> 00:30:05,849
Mr. Zhou.

609
00:30:05,970 --> 00:30:07,049
Yesterday, in the hospital,

610
00:30:07,049 --> 00:30:09,170
I saw Zhu Zhisheng's mom

611
00:30:09,170 --> 00:30:11,450
with an ambulance chaser
loitering in the hospital.

612
00:30:12,049 --> 00:30:14,250
I think that ambulance chaser is

613
00:30:14,250 --> 00:30:14,930
behind her timing

614
00:30:14,930 --> 00:30:16,730
(Ambulance chaser)
during Yiaiwan's IPO.

615
00:30:20,129 --> 00:30:22,569
Ambulance chasers
hunt hospital patients.

616
00:30:22,650 --> 00:30:24,210
They promise claim assistance,

617
00:30:24,210 --> 00:30:25,650
then fabricate evidence

618
00:30:25,730 --> 00:30:27,529
to extort huge insurance payouts

619
00:30:27,529 --> 00:30:29,129
before pocketing most

620
00:30:29,129 --> 00:30:29,849
of the settlement.

621
00:30:30,210 --> 00:30:30,730
I know.

622
00:30:32,890 --> 00:30:33,609
Hospital visit?

623
00:30:35,849 --> 00:30:37,369
But I didn't meet or speak

624
00:30:37,369 --> 00:30:38,529
with Zhu Zhisheng's mother

625
00:30:38,529 --> 00:30:40,089
or any other relatives.

626
00:30:41,609 --> 00:30:42,809
That ambulance chaser issue.

627
00:30:42,809 --> 00:30:44,529
I'll discuss it with Yiaiwan.

628
00:30:45,650 --> 00:30:46,730
But I should warn you.

629
00:30:47,490 --> 00:30:48,410
After years in law,

630
00:30:48,730 --> 00:30:50,170
you see humanity's extremes.

631
00:30:50,849 --> 00:30:51,890
Drive is good,

632
00:30:52,650 --> 00:30:54,650
but protect yourself first.

633
00:30:56,049 --> 00:30:56,609
Understood.

634
00:30:57,289 --> 00:30:57,896
Also,

635
00:30:58,529 --> 00:31:00,329
I accidentally saw

636
00:31:00,329 --> 00:31:03,089
sedative sleeping pills
by Zhu Zhisheng's bedside.

637
00:31:03,930 --> 00:31:04,490
So

638
00:31:04,970 --> 00:31:06,529
his coma is probably related to that.

639
00:31:08,289 --> 00:31:09,769
So now Zhu Zhisheng's coma

640
00:31:09,769 --> 00:31:11,769
probably has nothing
to do with Yiaiwan, right?

641
00:31:12,210 --> 00:31:12,890
The medicine

642
00:31:12,970 --> 00:31:15,369
is at most a possible
contributing factor to the coma.

643
00:31:15,730 --> 00:31:17,010
But what if he drank too?

644
00:31:18,010 --> 00:31:18,529
Drinking?

645
00:31:23,144 --> 00:31:26,289
(Yan Fei
to Ren Jiatong)

646
00:31:26,289 --> 00:31:26,952
Mr. Zhou.

647
00:31:27,890 --> 00:31:29,930
Will Yiaiwan still compensate him?

648
00:31:31,210 --> 00:31:31,970
What's your point?

649
00:31:32,890 --> 00:31:35,170
This might not be
a direct workplace injury,

650
00:31:35,730 --> 00:31:37,490
but we checked his clock-ins.

651
00:31:37,690 --> 00:31:39,569
He was grinding overtime constantly.

652
00:31:40,010 --> 00:31:40,609
Moreover,

653
00:31:41,010 --> 00:31:42,089
those pills

654
00:31:42,650 --> 00:31:44,650
were likely due to work stress.

655
00:31:45,210 --> 00:31:47,089
Giving zero compensation

656
00:31:47,089 --> 00:31:49,170
would be brutal for young employees.

657
00:31:55,129 --> 00:31:55,816
I'm sorry.

658
00:31:58,129 --> 00:31:59,210
I shouldn't have said that.

659
00:32:01,809 --> 00:32:02,410
No apologies.

660
00:32:03,369 --> 00:32:04,210
Emotionally,

661
00:32:04,210 --> 00:32:05,490
I understand your words.

662
00:32:06,490 --> 00:32:08,890
And I appreciate your passion.

663
00:32:09,529 --> 00:32:10,089
But,

664
00:32:10,970 --> 00:32:12,289
this isn't the right occasion

665
00:32:12,490 --> 00:32:13,890
nor the right time for those words.

666
00:32:14,410 --> 00:32:15,016
Understood?

667
00:32:16,250 --> 00:32:16,769
Understood.

668
00:32:17,930 --> 00:32:19,289
I won't say such things

669
00:32:19,289 --> 00:32:20,450
in professional settings.

670
00:32:22,289 --> 00:32:24,129
I'll go to that bartender again

671
00:32:24,129 --> 00:32:24,809
to find out more

672
00:32:24,809 --> 00:32:26,289
about Zhu Zhisheng's medication.

673
00:32:27,809 --> 00:32:28,329
I'll go too.

674
00:32:35,049 --> 00:32:36,049
Those words...

675
00:32:36,730 --> 00:32:38,250
Even if you care about Guo Xiaoyu,

676
00:32:38,250 --> 00:32:40,010
you wouldn't voice it professionally.

677
00:32:40,010 --> 00:32:40,648
Right?

678
00:32:40,849 --> 00:32:41,650
What's with you?

679
00:32:47,304 --> 00:32:49,512
(Emergency)

680
00:32:52,648 --> 00:32:54,344
(Esazolam Tablets:
Sedative, sleeping pills.)

681
00:32:54,344 --> 00:32:55,816
(Primarily used to treat
anxiety and insomnia)

682
00:32:55,816 --> 00:32:57,192
(and also tension, fear,
epilepsy and seizures.)

683
00:33:01,569 --> 00:33:03,809
I was remembering someone
and something from the past.

684
00:33:05,849 --> 00:33:07,289
I knew someone who,

685
00:33:08,170 --> 00:33:10,250
during stressful times, couldn't sleep

686
00:33:11,609 --> 00:33:12,730
and took similar medication.

687
00:33:22,329 --> 00:33:23,369
How did you discover

688
00:33:23,369 --> 00:33:25,010
Zhu Zhisheng drank before collapsing?

689
00:33:25,529 --> 00:33:26,690
Though I quit drinking,

690
00:33:26,730 --> 00:33:28,529
I'm still highly sensitive to alcohol.

691
00:33:28,930 --> 00:33:31,049
And I have a sommelier license,

692
00:33:31,210 --> 00:33:32,890
so I connected well with that bartender.

693
00:33:33,089 --> 00:33:34,730
It was only two days ago,

694
00:33:34,730 --> 00:33:35,769
during a big party night.

695
00:33:35,890 --> 00:33:36,849
Hard to forget easily.

696
00:33:37,369 --> 00:33:39,329
Why didn't you tell me
during our call last night?

697
00:33:39,730 --> 00:33:42,210
You didn't mention
anything to me either.

698
00:33:46,609 --> 00:33:47,970
I didn't tell you because...

699
00:33:51,930 --> 00:33:53,329
I'm not using this to compete

700
00:33:53,329 --> 00:33:54,210
against you.

701
00:33:58,569 --> 00:33:59,289
But I am.

702
00:34:02,769 --> 00:34:04,289
Since the moment I came to Hangzhou.

703
00:34:15,370 --> 00:34:16,729
I want to win. I won't deny it.

704
00:34:16,810 --> 00:34:18,970
But exposing the scumbag
who hurt my friend

705
00:34:18,970 --> 00:34:20,450
matters just as much to me.

706
00:34:20,890 --> 00:34:22,169
If Zhu doesn't get compensated,

707
00:34:22,169 --> 00:34:23,169
he deserves it.

708
00:34:23,609 --> 00:34:24,569
This isn't about you.

709
00:34:24,609 --> 00:34:26,729
He hurt Guo Xiaoyu first.

710
00:34:27,049 --> 00:34:27,609
I won't allow

711
00:34:27,609 --> 00:34:29,249
my friend to feel torn in the middle

712
00:34:29,249 --> 00:34:30,890
after being betrayed.

713
00:34:31,689 --> 00:34:33,330
Once I show her proof

714
00:34:33,330 --> 00:34:34,089
of his infidelity,

715
00:34:34,290 --> 00:34:35,290
she won't be conflicted.

716
00:34:35,649 --> 00:34:36,729
How can she handle that?

717
00:34:36,810 --> 00:34:38,569
Telling her now will devastate her.

718
00:34:38,649 --> 00:34:39,810
But even if it's painful,

719
00:34:39,810 --> 00:34:40,810
it's temporary.

720
00:34:40,810 --> 00:34:42,850
Better than her naively
going to the hospital daily,

721
00:34:42,850 --> 00:34:44,569
spending money and energy.

722
00:34:45,089 --> 00:34:47,010
After we settle Zhu Zhisheng's matter,

723
00:34:47,169 --> 00:34:48,249
we'll take her back.

724
00:34:49,089 --> 00:34:51,089
But we can't decide for Guo Xiaoyu

725
00:34:51,089 --> 00:34:52,529
which pain cuts deeper.

726
00:34:52,609 --> 00:34:53,450
We aren't her.

727
00:34:54,290 --> 00:34:56,209
Don't you know
how desperately she wants him

728
00:34:56,209 --> 00:34:57,209
to wake up?

729
00:34:57,609 --> 00:34:59,890
You're being contradictory.

730
00:35:00,049 --> 00:35:01,410
Which side are you even on?

731
00:35:01,689 --> 00:35:03,890
You uncovered
Zhu Zhisheng's sedative use.

732
00:35:03,970 --> 00:35:05,609
I found evidence of his drinking.

733
00:35:05,890 --> 00:35:07,529
We were cooperating well.

734
00:35:08,089 --> 00:35:09,649
You think I'm harming Guo Xiaoyu.

735
00:35:09,770 --> 00:35:10,330
And you?

736
00:35:18,410 --> 00:35:19,010
Xiaoyu.

737
00:35:23,450 --> 00:35:24,010
Why?

738
00:35:27,129 --> 00:35:27,720
Jiatong.

739
00:35:29,089 --> 00:35:30,609
You came to the hospital yesterday.

740
00:35:32,330 --> 00:35:34,169
Was it to see me or gather evidence?

741
00:35:36,569 --> 00:35:37,770
You saw it yesterday.

742
00:35:38,129 --> 00:35:39,169
He's suffering.

743
00:35:39,490 --> 00:35:40,490
And Ms. Wang,

744
00:35:40,810 --> 00:35:42,930
who raised her son
alone through hardship.

745
00:35:43,249 --> 00:35:44,970
Now, her only child is in a coma.

746
00:35:44,970 --> 00:35:46,330
Yiaiwan offers no response.

747
00:35:46,609 --> 00:35:48,370
For days, only a department lead visited

748
00:35:48,370 --> 00:35:50,129
and stayed for just 15 minutes.

749
00:35:50,850 --> 00:35:52,010
She wants an explanation.

750
00:35:52,010 --> 00:35:53,049
What's wrong with that?

751
00:35:53,370 --> 00:35:54,850
Why push them further?

752
00:35:57,930 --> 00:35:58,649
Guo Xiaoyu.

753
00:35:59,850 --> 00:36:01,209
Zhu Zhisheng did cheat.

754
00:36:02,410 --> 00:36:03,209
If you doubt it,

755
00:36:03,689 --> 00:36:04,689
we both have proof.

756
00:36:07,930 --> 00:36:08,569
You two

757
00:36:10,169 --> 00:36:10,770
knew all along?

758
00:36:14,770 --> 00:36:16,330
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

759
00:36:16,970 --> 00:36:18,410
Now that you know the truth,

760
00:36:18,649 --> 00:36:20,010
stop letting them deceive you.

761
00:36:23,209 --> 00:36:24,810
Yan Fei, I know you mean well.

762
00:36:26,890 --> 00:36:29,450
I don't want
to hold you back from your work.

763
00:36:30,169 --> 00:36:31,850
But now, Zhubao and Ms. Wang

764
00:36:31,850 --> 00:36:33,330
are completely cornered.

765
00:36:34,689 --> 00:36:36,450
Guo Xiaoyu, get a grip.

766
00:36:36,569 --> 00:36:39,129
He cheated first and hurt you.

767
00:36:39,450 --> 00:36:41,569
I despise these kinds
of scumbags more than anything.

768
00:36:42,010 --> 00:36:43,330
Besides, this is the truth.

769
00:36:43,569 --> 00:36:45,209
We haven't wrongfully accused him.

770
00:36:45,490 --> 00:36:47,850
Did this relationship
scramble your brain?

771
00:36:48,290 --> 00:36:49,209
This relationship

772
00:36:49,209 --> 00:36:51,049
lost its meaning

773
00:36:51,249 --> 00:36:52,450
the moment he cheated.

774
00:36:58,290 --> 00:36:59,850
After the hurt of betrayal,

775
00:37:00,689 --> 00:37:02,169
a relationship loses all meaning.

776
00:37:03,129 --> 00:37:04,010
What about us then?

777
00:37:10,890 --> 00:37:13,770
I snuck home this morning
while my parents were at work

778
00:37:14,370 --> 00:37:16,370
to cook this for you two.

779
00:37:27,649 --> 00:37:29,529
You both came all the way
to Hangzhou for me.

780
00:37:29,970 --> 00:37:32,370
That warms my heart deeply.

781
00:37:32,970 --> 00:37:34,290
But I also feel incredibly sorry.

782
00:37:36,850 --> 00:37:37,370
Jiatong.

783
00:37:38,930 --> 00:37:40,810
What I told you last night

784
00:37:41,689 --> 00:37:43,010
came straight from my heart.

785
00:37:45,850 --> 00:37:47,649
I truly see you both as my sisters.

786
00:37:51,089 --> 00:37:51,810
Xiaoyu.

787
00:37:57,810 --> 00:37:58,450
Xiaoyu.

788
00:37:58,770 --> 00:37:59,689
Xiaoyu, wait up.

789
00:38:04,616 --> 00:38:05,448
(Zhu Zhisheng's Collapse Claim)
Xiaoyu

790
00:38:05,770 --> 00:38:07,290
(Mrs. Zhu says Guo Xiaoyu shared company info.)
Yiaiwan's legal department

791
00:38:07,290 --> 00:38:09,529
received documents
from Zhu Zhisheng's mother.

792
00:38:09,609 --> 00:38:10,689
She says you told her

793
00:38:10,689 --> 00:38:12,010
about Yiaiwan's upcoming IPO.

794
00:38:12,609 --> 00:38:14,049
It's probably that ambulance chaser.

795
00:38:14,410 --> 00:38:16,330
He might have told Zhu's mother

796
00:38:16,330 --> 00:38:17,330
to frame you.

797
00:38:17,529 --> 00:38:18,970
Ms. Wang wouldn't say that.

798
00:38:19,410 --> 00:38:20,770
Could there be a misunderstanding?

799
00:38:27,330 --> 00:38:28,290
She also claims

800
00:38:28,290 --> 00:38:30,049
Jun An sent Zhu Zhisheng's girlfriend

801
00:38:30,049 --> 00:38:31,490
to negotiate with her

802
00:38:31,609 --> 00:38:32,689
to cover up

803
00:38:32,689 --> 00:38:34,689
Yiaiwan's forcing overtime
on Zhu Zhisheng

804
00:38:34,689 --> 00:38:35,569
to avoid paying.

805
00:38:36,330 --> 00:38:36,890
Ms. Wang,

806
00:38:37,609 --> 00:38:38,890
if Zhu Zhisheng's case

807
00:38:38,890 --> 00:38:40,569
is recognized as a work injury,

808
00:38:40,810 --> 00:38:43,010
he can claim workers' compensation.

809
00:38:47,810 --> 00:38:50,529
They sent over dashcam footage
and this photo.

810
00:39:01,384 --> 00:39:03,848
(Let's have a call
after your meeting, Ren Jiatong.)

811
00:39:04,410 --> 00:39:06,169
The calmer Ms. Bai sounds,

812
00:39:06,770 --> 00:39:07,330
the scarier.

813
00:39:07,810 --> 00:39:09,209
Ms. Bai is worried about you two.

814
00:39:10,089 --> 00:39:11,529
During our online meeting,

815
00:39:11,569 --> 00:39:12,490
she told Mr. Zhuang

816
00:39:12,490 --> 00:39:13,689
Guo Xiaoyu was unaware then.

817
00:39:14,089 --> 00:39:15,850
Her legal advice in the car was given

818
00:39:15,850 --> 00:39:17,209
before our meeting started.

819
00:39:17,649 --> 00:39:19,569
It was just general legal counsel,

820
00:39:19,930 --> 00:39:21,049
not reflecting Jun An.

821
00:39:21,649 --> 00:39:22,810
Mr. Song also defended you,

822
00:39:23,010 --> 00:39:24,370
saying you reported the conflict

823
00:39:24,649 --> 00:39:25,450
and stayed clear.

824
00:39:25,770 --> 00:39:27,410
But I never reported to Mr. Song.

825
00:39:27,770 --> 00:39:28,609
You reported to me,

826
00:39:28,890 --> 00:39:29,770
and I told Mr. Song.

827
00:39:31,450 --> 00:39:32,290
Thank you, Mr. Zhou.

828
00:39:33,890 --> 00:39:34,970
I was overwhelmed that day.

829
00:39:35,450 --> 00:39:37,049
Your timely reminder saved me.

830
00:39:38,010 --> 00:39:38,600
Mr. Zhou,

831
00:39:39,209 --> 00:39:41,249
is this photo the biggest headache?

832
00:39:43,249 --> 00:39:46,209
But we've never discussed
this matter with Zhu Zhisheng's mother.

833
00:39:47,010 --> 00:39:48,010
I believe you.

834
00:39:48,890 --> 00:39:51,010
But photos can
be interpreted too broadly.

835
00:39:51,410 --> 00:39:52,930
Prepare yourselves mentally

836
00:39:53,490 --> 00:39:54,370
for potential trouble.

837
00:39:58,649 --> 00:39:59,810
I'll talk to Ms. Wang.

838
00:40:00,129 --> 00:40:01,290
She did this because she felt

839
00:40:01,290 --> 00:40:01,850
cornered.

840
00:40:01,850 --> 00:40:02,770
She's not a bad person.

841
00:40:03,169 --> 00:40:04,330
And you still trust her?

842
00:40:04,850 --> 00:40:05,450
If you go,

843
00:40:05,450 --> 00:40:07,129
what if she records you again?

844
00:40:10,290 --> 00:40:10,984
Mr. Zhou,

845
00:40:11,209 --> 00:40:12,490
let's go to the hospital

846
00:40:12,529 --> 00:40:13,930
